Detailed Description

Base class for OBEX clients within applications.

ObexClient::ObexClient (  ExecutionContext *  ctx_ptr  ) 
 

Constructor. Constructs a usable object instance.

Intended to be used with dynamically allocated objects (new).

Parameters:
ctx_ptr Execution context in which the client is to be run. You may pass '0' as actual parameter to specify the current execution context. In the latter case, the current context must be valid at construction time.
